reviewText: It was excellent. I teach a ladies Sunday school class for senior adults.  I try to have materials they can enjoy at home.

I bought this and one other Ken Davis video to show to my high school sunday school class. (That way they get a break from me!) I like his humor and the way he relates scriptural events to our lives. Good for high school age through adult. I recommend it.

We love Ken Davis in person, he is a great comedienne.  We wanted to be entertained like when  he is live and it was good but more like a church service.  Our problem because we thought everything he did was funny.
